description:
AJKB-04 EMBROIDERED NET 3 PCS

By Pcs: 3 Pcs Peshwas: Net Trouser: Silk Dupatta: Net Color: Green

Wrapped in the soft, muted shades of green, this ensemble embodies a quiet elegance. Adorned with delicate golden lurex and beige threads, the fabric glistens with dew-like silver sequins in 9mm and 5mm sizes, capturing a gentle shimmer. The embroidered dupatta, a sheer veil of beauty, crowns this nature-inspired creation, promising a look that captivates with understated grace and leaves an unforgettable impression.
DESIGN DETAILS:

Pair of embroidered front bodice (right & left) on net
Embroidered back bodice on net
16 embroidered Kalis for peshwas on net
4.5 meter embroidered border for ghera on net
Pair of embroidered sleeves on net
2.5 meter embroidered dupatta with 4-side border on net
1.5 meter wide-width silk for trouser
